SpringMVC03_02 Spring Setting Order

1. pom.xml
	add ojdbc6,
	add dbcp(commons),
	add mybatis,
	add mybatis-spring,
	add spring-orm
	
2. web.xml
	encodingFilter Setting
	
3. myboard.sql (경로 : WEB-INF/spring/sqls/myboard.sql)

4. BoardDto, BoardDao(Impl), BoardBiz(Impl), Controller (경로 : src/main/java)

5. mybaits setting. board-mapper.xml (src/main/resources/mybaits/board-mapper.xml)

6. db.properties (경로 : src/main/resources/mybaits/db.properties)

7. config.xml (경로 : src/main/resources/WEB-INF/spring/sqls/config.xml)

9. applicationContext.xml setting